注意分散 散开 散开！
Get separation. Track away, track away!

1862
01:52:12,930 --> 01:52:14,800
往左转 往左转！
Hard left! Hard left!

1863
01:52:16,060 --> 01:52:18,010
六百英尺
Six hundred feet.

1864
