你们快看！
Guys, look!

1892
01:54:27,940 --> 01:54:30,600
- 来了 敌机来了！ - 大家隐蔽！
- Incoming, incoming! - Everybody hide!

1893
01:54:58,760 --> 01:55:01,050
别动
Don't move.

1894
01:55:06,270 --> 01:55:07,480
来吧
Go, go.

1895
01:55:14,490 --> 01:55:15,520
快跑！
Run!

1896
