火力掩护！
Cover fire!

1897
01:55:19,490 --> 01:55:22,860
打破玻璃！ 跳窗！
Shoot the glass! Jump out the window!

1898
01:55:29,330 --> 01:55:30,410
跳！
Jump!

1899
01:55:46,350 --> 01:55:49,840
我们要死了！
We're gonna die!

1900
01:55:51,400 --> 01:55:53,260
山姆 我停不下来！
Sam, I can't stop!

1901
01:55:53,690 --> 01:55:55,560
打碎玻璃！
Shoot the glass!

1902
01:56:21,220 --> 01:56:22,300
山姆！
Sam!

1903
01:56:47,790 --> 01:56:50,120
大家没事吧？
Is everybody okay?

1904
01:56:50,210 --> 01:56:51,240
你没事吧？
You okay?

1905
