那鬼东西是什么？
What the hell was that?

1906
01:56:52,920 --> 01:56:55,880
钻孔机器人饥渴了
Driller-bot is thirsty.

1907
01:56:59,260 --> 01:57:01,250
- 那个独眼恶魔正在看着我！- 什么？
- This evil thing's looking at me! - What?

1908
01:57:14,270 --> 01:57:16,480
他还带了个蚯蚓一样的霸天虎！
It's even got an uglier Decepticon with it!

1909
01:57:16,570 --> 01:57:17,810
不得不撤离！
We have to evac!

1910
01:57:36,420 --> 01:57:40,130
- 艾普斯中士 楼梯已经被堵住了！ - 我们被困住了！
- Sergeant Epps, the stairs are blocked! - We're trapped!

1911
01:57:40,630 --> 01:57:42,840
我们怎么从这里出去？嘿 快点！
Okay. How do we get out of here? Hey! Come on!

1912
01:57:42,930 --> 01:57:45,210
噢 主啊 只要让我活着逃出去
Oh, Lord Jesus, let me just get out of this alive.

1913
01:57:56,020 --> 01:57:57,730
快 得马上撤！
Move! We got to move!

1914
01:57:57,820 --> 01:57:59,930
霸天虎怎么老是有那么厉害的玩意？
Why do the Decepticons always get the good shit?

1915
01:58:00,030 --> 01:58:01,860
- 快跑！ - 我们要被吃了
- Move! - We're about to be eaten, people!

1916
01:58:24,380 --> 01:58:26,170
我们要死了！
We're gonna die!

1917
01:58:41,940 --> 01:58:44,280
- 抓紧！ - 把你的手给我！
- Hold on! - Give me your hand!

1918
01:58:44,450 --> 01:58:45,940
- 我来摇荡一下！ - 抓紧她！
- I'm swinging that way! - Got her!

1919
01:58:46,030 --> 01:58:47,570
哦 天啊！
Oh, my God!

1920
01:58:47,660 --> 01:58:50,020
把她丢到防火梯那里！
I'm dropping you on the fire escape!

1921
01:59:07,430 --> 01:59:08,460
山姆！
Sam!

1922
01:59:09,720 --> 01:59:11,590
离开这里！
We gotta move!

1923
01:59:24,820 --> 01:59:27,610
我来救你们了！
I'm coming for you!

1924
02:00:22,540 --> 02:00:23,880
擎天柱！
Optimus!

1925
02:00:23,960 --> 02:00:26,620
- 雷霆拯救队！ - 我们来了！
- Wreckers! - We're coming!

1926
02:00:27,800 --> 02:00:30,670
世界各地的霸天虎
Decepticons around the world,

1927
02:00:30,760 --> 02:00:32,720
发射能量柱
launch the pillars.

1928
02:01:03,670 --> 02:01:06,080
我们又迷路了！
We are so lost!

1929
02:01:06,170 --> 02:01:07,500
总是被遗忘
Always left out.

1930
02:01:08,670 --> 02:01:10,410
太棒了！
Ka-ching!

1931
02:01:12,590 --> 02:01:14,330
也该轮到咱们发号施令了
It's time to lay down the law.

1932
02:01:14,430 --> 02:01:15,970
即将搞点破坏啥的
About to bring some hurt now.

1933
