我就让你干护送这一件事
I give you one thing to do,

1938
02:01:53,470 --> 02:01:55,420
做一件事 你都能搞砸了？
one thing to do, and you drop the ball on that?

1939
02:01:55,510 --> 02:01:57,130
我可没答应做所有事！
I ain't signed up for all this!

1940
02:01:57,220 --> 02:01:59,430
外星人朝我轰炸 东奔西跑 追个不停！
Got aliens blasting at me, running around, chasing me!

1941
02:01:59,520 --> 02:02:01,760
我在教堂和建筑之间四处躲避并挣扎逃命！
I'm ducking through churches and buildings and all that kind of crap!

1942
02:02:01,850 --> 02:02:04,810
都是胡说！我可没答应这些干这个 艾普斯
This is bullshit! I ain't signed up for this, Epps.

1943
02:02:04,900 --> 02:02:06,060
我尽力不再吵了
I'm trying to keep it together.

1944
02:02:10,280 --> 02:02:13,860
- 真难得！只有你和我了！ - 卡莉！
- What a treat! You and me, alone! - Carly!

1945
02:02:19,240 --> 02:02:20,730
快 快！快逃！
Come on, come on! Run!

1946
02:02:23,160 --> 02:02:25,950
他是冲着我来的 不是你
Okay. He's after me, not you.

1947
02:02:26,580 --> 02:02:27,920
快跑！
Run!

1948
02:02:29,420 --> 02:02:31,830
你无处可藏了 小子！
You can't hide, boy!

1949
