Target the Decepticon!

1956
02:03:31,820 --> 02:03:33,020
山姆！
Sam!

1957
02:03:37,990 --> 02:03:39,350
伦诺克斯上校 你们快救救山姆！
Please, you've got to save Sam!

1958
02:03:39,450 --> 02:03:40,860
