1970
02:04:20,240 --> 02:04:22,070
还有多少时间？
How long do we have?

1971
02:04:22,870 --> 02:04:25,650
我要宰了你们！
I'm gonna kick you!

1972
02:04:34,210 --> 02:04:35,620
割 割 割！
Cut, cut, cut!

1973
02:04:37,090 --> 02:04:39,210
我要杀…
I'm gonna kill...

1974
02:04:56,070 --> 02:04:58,020
他死掉了
Well, he's dead.

1975
