它把我们吸进来了！我也不想这样！
It sucked me in! There was nothing I could do!

1978
02:05:37,320 --> 02:05:38,930
这下麻烦大了…
This is a total cluster...

1979
02:05:39,610 --> 02:05:42,100
我们必须过河
We got to get across the river.

1980
