2012
02:07:07,480 --> 02:07:09,530
狙击手 射瞎他们的眼睛
Snipers, shoot for the eyes.

2013
02:07:09,530 --> 02:07:12,200
目标就在那栋建筑的顶部 现在出击
All right, your target is up on top of that building, that cupola.

2014
02:07:12,540 --> 02:07:15,280
你们太愚蠢了 汽车人
How doomed you are, Autobots.

2015
02:07:15,370 --> 02:07:17,790
连这么简单的道理都不懂
You simply fail to understand

2016
02:07:17,880 --> 02:07:22,210
少数人的利益必须服从大众的需求
that the needs of the many outweigh the needs of the few.

2017
02:07:22,510 --> 02:07:25,040
启动太空桥
Activating the bridge.

2018
02:07:36,560 --> 02:07:38,390
他们好像在守卫什么东西
They happy about something.

2019
02:07:38,770 --> 02:07:40,640
我们已经到了他们母舰的中心
We're in the heart of their ship.

2020
02:07:40,730 --> 02:07:42,690
让咱们帮他们开一会儿
Let's give 'em a little ride.

2021
02:07:42,780 --> 02:07:45,110
让我们来把这船掀个底朝天
We gonna screw this ship up.

2022
02:07:45,490 --> 02:07:47,900
这是128位的二进制密码
It's a 128K binary encryption code.

2023
02:07:49,240 --> 02:07:50,900
很难破解
It's difficult.

2024
02:07:51,490 --> 02:07:54,480
但不适用于我 我进去了 放下吊桥
But not for me. I'm in. Bridge down.

2025
02:07:56,000 --> 02:07:58,410
桥面被放下来了！有人在暗中帮助我们！
The bridge is coming down! Someone's watching over us!

2026
02:07:59,040 --> 02:08:00,580
快点！出发！
Come on! Let's go!

2027
02:08:00,790 --> 02:08:03,280
“很荣幸能跟你合作 西摩”
"Pleasure working with you, Seymour."

2028
02:08:03,380 --> 02:08:05,090
我相信你会这么说的
I believe you're supposed to say.

2029
02:08:05,920 --> 02:08:07,410
做得好 达奇
Good job, Dutch.

2030
02:08:07,420 --> 02:08:08,520
（非常感谢（荷兰语））

2031
02:08:14,270 --> 02:08:15,850
放开我！
Get off me!

2032
02:08:40,670 --> 02:08:43,250
快点！他们正在启动能量柱！
Hurry! They're triggering the pillars!

2033
02:08:44,500 --> 02:08:46,660
战俘？ 你们还收战俘？
Prisoners? You're keeping prisoners?

2034
02:08:47,010 --> 02:08:48,960
是的
Yes.

2035
02:08:49,180 --> 02:08:50,790
你得教他们学乖点
You need to teach them about respect.

2036
02:08:51,140 --> 02:08:53,380
以前是公事公办 现在是私人恩怨 你懂我的意思吗？
This was all business, but now it's personal, do you understand me?

2037
02:08:54,970 --> 02:08:59,970
我懂 没有战俘 只有战利品
I understand. No prisoners, only trophies.

2038
02:09:00,810 --> 02:09:04,430
大黄蜂 我觉得他们想要杀了我们…
Bee, I think they're going to kill us.

2039
02:09:05,480 --> 02:09:08,730
- 你 你的死期到了 - 等等 等等！
- You, your time is up. - Wait, wait, wait!

2040
02:09:08,820 --> 02:09:11,110
我们投降了！我们是战俘
We surrendered! We're your prisoners.

2041
02:09:11,200 --> 02:09:13,400
- 快走！ - 我们就不能谈谈吗？
- Move it! - Can't we talk this out?

2042
02:09:13,490 --> 02:09:17,110
我们全都是好小子！我是说…
We're all a bunch of good chaps! I mean you no...

2043
02:09:19,830 --> 02:09:21,870
为什么…
Why did you...

2044
02:09:28,970 --> 02:09:30,960
再见了 我的老朋友
Good-bye, my old friend.

2045
02:09:32,180 --> 02:09:34,010
现在 你是我的了！
You're mine now.

2046
02:09:47,530 --> 02:09:48,860
别碰我！
Get off me!

2047
02:09:49,530 --> 02:09:50,980
- 我得去救他 - 什么？
- I got to help him. - What?

2048
02:09:51,820 --> 02:09:53,280
你在干什么？
What are you doing?

2049
02:09:53,360 --> 02:09:55,860
- 我要去救他 - 山姆 你救不了的
- I got to help him. - Sam, you can't help him.

2050
02:10:03,870 --> 02:10:06,120
转过身去
Turn around.

2051
02:10:15,050 --> 02:10:17,630
我们… 我们曾有过很多的回忆
We... We gave 'em a hell of a run.

2052
02:10:33,570 --> 02:10:35,190
成功了 聪明鬼！我们成功了！
We did it, Brains! We did it!

2053
02:10:35,280 --> 02:10:36,820
把飞船拆成废铁吧！
Rip this ship apart!

2054
02:11:15,450 --> 02:11:17,200
- 我们干得真棒 聪明鬼 你和我 - 是啊
- We had a nice run, Brains, you and me. - Yeah,

2055
02:11:17,250 --> 02:11:18,220
不过我们死定了
we gonna die.

2056
02:11:34,760 --> 02:11:37,460
哇 哇 哇！好了宝贝！跟我们一起来吧！
Whoa, whoa, whoa! Okay, baby! You all come with us!

2057
02:11:38,140 --> 02:11:40,840
我们走！你们跟紧地面部队！走！
Go! You guys, follow that ground team! Go!

2058
02:11:40,930 --> 02:11:41,500
快 快 快走！
Move, move, move!

2059
02:11:41,660 --> 02:11:44,500
艾普斯 你们上3楼！我们要上45楼！
Epps, third floor! We're going to 45!

2060
02:11:49,810 --> 02:11:51,430
你们两个狙击手留在这里！
All right. Two snipers, right here!

2061
02:11:53,480 --> 02:11:54,470
报告位置！
All right, dock up!

2062
02:11:56,110 --> 02:11:57,980
3分钟后就跳伞！
We jump in three minutes!

2063
02:12:01,080 --> 02:12:02,990
安置火力点 这边
Set up shop right here.

2064
02:12:07,580 --> 02:12:08,700
各就各位
Set up.

2065
02:12:10,630 --> 02:12:11,990
在楼下
I'm downstairs.

2066
02:12:12,090 --> 02:12:14,670
有5个目标 还有震荡波 就在我们脚下
We got five targets and Shockwave right below us.

2067
02:12:14,920 --> 02:12:16,660
准备跳伞！
Stand by to jump!

2068
02:12:16,760 --> 02:12:19,090
好了 我们走！准备 准备
All right, let's go! Get ready, get ready.

2069
02:12:32,400 --> 02:12:34,010
出发！
Go!

2070
02:12:43,870 --> 02:12:45,610
狙击手 敲了他们的眼睛
Snipers, take out their eyes.

2071
02:12:49,370 --> 02:12:50,860
好了 爆破组 安装炸弹
All right, demo team, let's crank steel.

2072
02:12:59,090 --> 02:13:01,130
即时引爆！
Turning steel!

2073
02:13:37,250 --> 02:13:38,660
没我命令不准开火！
Don't fire till I tell you!

2074
02:13:49,520 --> 02:13:50,930
快！
Go!

2075
02:13:52,810 --> 02:13:54,350
干得不错！
Good job, kid!

2076
02:13:54,440 --> 02:13:55,470
开火！
Fire!

2077
02:14:07,740 --> 02:14:09,280
- 我们打到他了！ - 是啊！
- We got him!     - Yeah!

2078
02:14:10,450 --> 02:14:12,070
他在逃跑！
He's on the run!

2079
02:14:14,420 --> 02:14:16,500
汽车人 攻击！
Autobots, attack!

2080
02:14:21,800 --> 02:14:23,760
火力集中到桥上！
Mortar that bridge!

2081
02:14:27,430 --> 02:14:29,760
现在这是我们的世界了！
It's our world now!

2082
02:14:30,640 --> 02:14:32,630
开始传送！
Commence transport!

2083
02:14:44,660 --> 02:14:47,270
哦 天啊 天啊
Oh, my God. Oh, my God.

2084
02:15:01,920 --> 02:15:03,250
擎天柱！
Optimus!

2085
02:15:38,210 --> 02:15:40,200
去死吧！
You die!

2086
02:15:48,220 --> 02:15:49,500
不！
No!

2087
02:16:00,110 --> 02:16:02,390
给我下来 御天敌！
Get down here, Sentinel!

2088
02:16:02,480 --> 02:16:04,570
擎天柱
Optimus,

2089
02:16:04,650 --> 02:16:06,560
你忘了你的立场！
you forget your place!

2090
02:16:13,410 --> 02:16:17,070
我给你带来了塞伯坦 你的故乡
I bring you Cybertron, your home,

2091
02:16:17,920 --> 02:16:21,080
你依然要站在人类那边吗？
and still you choose humanity.

2092
02:16:21,170 --> 02:16:25,080
是你教会我自由权利归众生
You were the one who taught me freedom is everyone's right.

2093
02:16:28,590 --> 02:16:30,830
我会重启能量柱！
I will retrigger that pillar!

2094
02:16:30,930 --> 02:16:34,010
那你得先过我这关！
Then you'll have to go through me!

2095
02:16:38,020 --> 02:16:39,510
听着 我得去帮忙
Okay, I've got to try and help.

2096
02:16:39,600 --> 02:16:41,510
- 我自己去 你留在这里 - 你别去 别去
- I have to. You stay here. - Don't you go. Don't go.

2097
02:16:41,610 --> 02:16:44,970
你会没事的好吗？我保证 我得到主控能量柱那去
You'll be fine, okay? I promise. I got to get to that pillar.

2098
02:16:47,240 --> 02:16:49,070
拿下能量柱！
Charge the pillar!

2099
02:16:49,150 --> 02:16:50,490
汽车人来了！
We got Autobots!

2100
02:17:07,800 --> 02:17:09,750
我需要支援！
Reinforcements!

2101
02:17:09,840 --> 02:17:12,680
霸天虎飞船 向擎天柱开火！
Decepticon ships, fire at Optimus!

2102
02:17:17,220 --> 02:17:19,890
发射！我现在就需要那些战斧导弹！
We're taking fire! I need those Tomahawks now!

2103
02:17:20,140 --> 02:17:21,760
第一波导弹即将到达
First wave inbound.

2104
02:17:27,900 --> 02:17:30,520
我们必须掩护擎天柱！
We've got to cover for Optimus!

2105
02:17:44,670 --> 02:17:47,830
霸天虎！ 夺回能量柱！
Decepticons, trigger the pillar!

2106
02:17:48,550 --> 02:17:50,540
重启能量柱！
Restart that pillar!

2107
02:17:51,010 --> 02:17:52,420
启动那根能量柱
Trigger the pillars.

2108
02:17:53,300 --> 02:17:57,550
我挡不住了！我需要躲避一下！
I can't hold them! The ships have us pinned!

2109
02:17:58,270 --> 02:17:59,680
不！
No!

2110
02:18:00,020 --> 02:18:02,550
导弹到达 还有10秒！危险接近！
Inbound, 10 seconds! Danger close!

2111
02:18:02,640 --> 02:18:04,930
解码M-L-E-F 14250！
Mark-Lima-Echo-Echo, 14250!

2112
02:18:05,020 --> 02:18:06,260
确信表面接触
Positive surface contact.

2113
02:18:06,360 --> 02:18:07,850
- 请给座标 - 已获取目标
- Target I.D. - Target acquired.

2114
02:18:36,430 --> 02:18:39,010
- 迪伦！等等！ - 不！
- Dylan! Wait! - No!

2115
02:18:42,020 --> 02:18:43,050
迪伦！
Dylan!

2116
02:18:44,140 --> 02:18:45,550
住手！住手！
Stop! Stop!

2117
02:18:45,900 --> 02:18:47,140
不！
No!

2118
02:18:47,730 --> 02:18:49,640
你不能这样做 好吗？
You can't do this, okay?

2119
02:18:50,280 --> 02:18:52,230
对我来说只有一个未来
There's only one future for me.

2120
02:19:16,180 --> 02:19:17,900
塞伯坦
Cybertron,

2121
02:19:17,960 --> 02:19:20,580
你终于得救了
you are saved,

2122
02:19:20,590 --> 02:19:22,460
在最后时刻
at last.

2123
02:19:31,530 --> 02:19:34,640
你是来向我投降的吗？
Have you come to surrender?

2124
02:19:35,070 --> 02:19:37,480
- 这一切都值得吗？ - 当然了
- Was it all worth it? - Obviously.

2125
02:19:37,570 --> 02:19:39,610
你费尽心机救回了御天敌
All your work to bring Sentinel back

2126
02:19:39,710 --> 02:19:41,700
而现在他却夺走了你所有的权力
and now clearly he has all the power.

2127
02:19:41,990 --> 02:19:43,780
我都有点替你感到难过了
It's actually almost tragic.

2128
02:19:43,870 --> 02:19:46,990
你胆敢教训我 奴隶？
You dare lecture me, slave?

2129
02:19:47,080 --> 02:19:49,660
就算你的霸天虎最终征服这个星球
Your Decepticons finally conquering this planet,

2130
02:19:49,750 --> 02:19:51,080
他们的领袖也不会是你
and yet, their leader won't be you!

2131
02:19:51,170 --> 02:19:55,500
一定是我！ 永远是我！
It will be me! It will always be me.

2132
02:19:56,590 --> 02:19:58,670
再过个几分钟
In any minute now,

2133
02:19:58,760 --> 02:20:02,590
除了当御天敌的婊子你什么都不是
you'll be nothing but Sentinel's bitch.

2134
02:20:09,770 --> 02:20:11,430
小心
Rock et!

2135
02:20:12,900 --> 02:20:14,110
去死！
Die!

2136
02:20:26,660 --> 02:20:27,990
你在选阵营时
You chose sides?

2137
02:20:29,120 --> 02:20:30,160
选错了
You chose wrong.

2138
02:20:36,340 --> 02:20:39,170
你一直是我们中最勇敢的战士
Always the bravest of us!

2139
02:20:42,180 --> 02:20:44,720
但你总是无法做出艰难抉择
But you could never make the hard decisions!

2140
02:20:47,770 --> 02:20:50,810
我们的星球会生存下去
Our planet will survive!

2141
02:20:51,770 --> 02:20:52,980
不！
No!

2142
02:21:02,870 --> 02:21:05,900
我们曾经是神 我们全都是
We were gods once. All of us.

2143
02:21:06,040 --> 02:21:08,370
- 但在这里… - 求你住手！
- But here...     - Please!

2144
02:21:08,460 --> 02:21:10,870
神只能有一个！
...there will only be one!

2145
02:21:21,800 --> 02:21:25,510
这是我的星球！
This is my planet!

2146
02:21:36,230 --> 02:21:38,190
我刚刚拯救了另一个世界！
I just saved a whole other world.

2147
02:21:38,400 --> 02:21:41,240
你以为你是英雄？你以为你是个英雄吗？
You think you're a hero, huh? You think you're a hero?

2148
02:21:41,570 --> 02:21:44,030
不 我只不过是个送信的
No. I'm just a messenger.

2149
02:21:51,420 --> 02:21:53,120
太空桥仍然连接着！
The pillar's still connected!

2150
02:21:55,040 --> 02:21:56,450
小心点！
Bring it up!

2151
02:21:56,750 --> 02:21:58,960
- 大黄蜂！开始干吧！ - 来吧 来吧！动手 动手！
- Bee! Let's do this! - Let's go, let's go! Move, move!

2152
02:21:59,050 --> 02:22:00,660
它仍在运作！
Pillar's still connected!

2153
02:22:00,760 --> 02:22:03,000
摧毁那根能量柱！
Rip that pillar down!

2154
02:22:26,280 --> 02:22:30,030
现在 我们应该停战
Now, we need a truce.

2155
02:22:30,120 --> 02:22:33,530
我只不过想重掌领导权
All I want is to be back in charge.

2156
02:22:33,620 --> 02:22:35,710
此外…
Besides,

2157
02:22:35,790 --> 02:22:39,580
没有我你能做什么 擎天柱？
who would you be without me, Prime?

2158
02:22:39,670 --> 02:22:42,080
咱们走着瞧
Time to find out.

2159
02:23:04,610 --> 02:23:07,730
擎天柱 我所想要的
Optimus, all I ever wanted

2160
02:23:07,820 --> 02:23:10,320
不过是我们种族的延续
was the survival of our race.

2161
02:23:10,740 --> 02:23:15,080
你必须明白 我不得不背叛你的原因
You must see why I had to betray you.

2162
02:23:15,170 --> 02:23:17,500
你并没有背叛我
You didn't betray me.

2163
02:23:18,000 --> 02:23:20,330
你背叛了你自己
You betrayed yourself.

2164
02:23:20,670 --> 02:23:22,210
不 擎天柱！
No, Optimus!

2165
02:24:18,400 --> 02:24:19,980
山姆
Sam.

2166
02:24:59,270 --> 02:25:02,100
我爱你
I love you.

2167
02:25:03,480 --> 02:25:04,720
在这世上我只需要你
You're the only thing I need in this world,

2168
02:25:04,820 --> 02:25:07,430
我会为你做任何事 我保证
and I'll do anything to make it up to you, I promise.

2169
02:25:08,070 --> 02:25:10,690
你可要信守承诺
I'm going to hold you to that.

2170
02:25:10,780 --> 02:25:12,270
不要再放我走了
Just never let me go.

2171
02:25:13,200 --> 02:25:14,820
我保证
I promise.

2172
02:25:20,120 --> 02:25:21,580
戒指？
Rings.

2173
02:25:29,380 --> 02:25:30,960
我爱这辆车！
I love this car.

2174
02:25:31,260 --> 02:25:33,050
大黄蜂 你得悠着点
Bee, you've got to slow it down.

2175
02:25:33,150 --> 02:25:35,200
悠着点来 好吗？
You got to slow way down, okay?

2176
02:25:35,930 --> 02:25:37,170
我只想帮个忙 老兄
I'm just trying to help out.

2177
02:25:39,310 --> 02:25:40,970
战争之中
In any war

2178
02:25:41,100 --> 02:25:44,090
总会有暴风雨之间的平静
there are calms between storms.

2179
02:25:44,810 --> 02:25:46,020
你小子很勇敢
You fought bravely.

2180
02:25:46,110 --> 02:25:48,720
有时候我们会失去信念
There will be days when we lose faith.

2181
02:25:48,820 --> 02:25:51,650
有时候我们的盟友会背叛我们
Days when our allies turn against us.

2182
02:25:52,320 --> 02:25:56,740
但是我们绝对不会放弃地球
But the day will never come that we forsake this planet

2183
02:25:56,990 --> 02:25:58,480
和地球上的人类
and its people.

2184
02:25:58,500 --> 02:26:06,680
是否你感到冰冷无助？
<i><b>Do you feel cold <i><b>and lost in desperation</b></i>

2185
02:26:06,690 --> 02:26:14,380
你满怀希望但最终充满绝望
<i><b>You build up hope <i><b>but failure's all you've known</b></i>

2186
02:26:14,510 --> 02:26:19,990
让这些不快逝去
<i><b>And let it go</b></i>

2187
02:26:20,810 --> 02:26:25,020
我的美好未来就从这一刻开始
That's what I call the start of a beautiful future.

2188
02:26:26,190 --> 02:26:28,150
逮捕他
Arrest him.

2189
02:26:28,320 --> 02:26:29,350
我够本了！
It was worth it!

2190
02:26:29,440 --> 02:26:31,520
- 把他带走！ - 我愿意为爱坐牢！我不在乎！
- Get him out of here! - I'd go to jail for love! I don't care!

2191
02:26:31,740 --> 02:26:34,600
开始吧 送我进去！我想坐牢！我想进去
Go ahead, take me in! I want to go in! Let's go in.

2192
02:26:34,700 --> 02:26:36,530
